    "rationale": "All 7 assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. Six factors are appropriately scoped out at MRL 2 per ASME V&V 40-2018 Table 3. CFD model demonstrates sufficient credibility to support the regulatory decision that the device's worst-case hemolysis operating condition produces RH < 1 relative to the predicate device. Project requirements documented in the design history file support this determination.",
